@startuml seq_summary_flow
title Live Summary Flow — Transcript → Key Points → Clients

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Transcriber\n(Audio Hijack)" as Transcriber
participant "Transcript\nFile (.txt)" as File
participant "Local Agent\n(quiz_daemon.py)" as Agent
participant "Claude API\n(Anthropic)" as Claude
participant "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
participant "Host UI\n(host.js)" as HostUI
participant "Participant UI\n(participant.js)" as PaxUI

== 1. Transcription (continuous) ==

Transcriber -> File : Appends speech segments\n(timestamped lines)
note right of File
  Format: [HH:MM:SS.xx] Speaker:\ttext
  Agent also appends heartbeat
  timestamps every 3s
end note

== 2. Periodic Summary Generation (every 5 min) ==

Agent -> File : Read last 30 min\nof transcript
Agent -> Agent : Build prompt:\nsession notes +\nexisting bullets +\ntranscript excerpt

Agent -> Claude : messages.create(\n  model="claude-sonnet-4-6",\n  max_tokens=1024,\n  system=SUMMARY_PROMPT\n)
Claude --> Agent : JSON array of\n5–15 bullet strings

Agent -> Agent : Prepend "Session date: YYYY-MM-DD"\nParse & validate response

== 3. Push to Server ==

Agent -> Backend : POST /api/summary\n{points: ["...", "..."]}\n(HTTP Basic Auth)
Backend -> Backend : state.summary_points = points\nstate.summary_updated_at = now()

== 4. Broadcast to Clients (WebSocket) ==

Backend --> HostUI : WS message type="state"\n{summary_points: [...],\nsummary_updated_at: "ISO8601"}
Backend --> PaxUI : WS message type="state"\n{summary_points: [...],\nsummary_updated_at: "ISO8601"}

HostUI -> HostUI : Badge → "🧠 Key Points (N)"\n(green, clickable → modal)
PaxUI -> PaxUI : Show 📋 button\n(click → modal with bullets)

== 5. Force Generation (host-initiated) ==

HostUI -> HostUI : Host clicks\n"🧠 No key points yet"
note right of HostUI
  Badge changes to
  "🧠 Generating..." (yellow)
end note

HostUI -> Backend : POST /api/summary/force
Backend -> Backend : state.summary_force_requested = true

Agent -> Backend : GET /api/summary/force\n(polled every ~1s)
Backend --> Agent : {requested: true}\n(flag reset to false)

Agent -> File : Read last 30 min\nof transcript
Agent -> Claude : messages.create()\n(same as periodic flow)
Claude --> Agent : JSON bullet array

Agent -> Backend : POST /api/summary\n{points: [...]}
Backend --> HostUI : WS broadcast: state
Backend --> PaxUI : WS broadcast: state

HostUI -> HostUI : Badge → "🧠 Key Points (N)"\n(green)

@enduml
